description:

My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, and families (with kids)

It's my home - enjoy comfortable bed, full kitchen with supplies that can be used, just please replace. 
There is a cute vintage bike that you're welcome to use, just take care as if was yours - any damage or loss a $ 500 will be charged. 
No closet space, or drawer space as they're full.

I'm available for any urgent matter and also keep in mind this is a doorman building with maintenance on site from Monday - Friday in case any adjustment is necessary.

hosts.about:
I'm Brazilian Born, New Yorker by heart! L-O-V-E travel and people.
I want that the guest feel like home and mainly do not have to deal with normal headaches of New York old buildings like mice, colder apartments with failure A/C and heat. When I travel I like comfort and I want that my guests feel comfortable with a bright and airy apartment, with a an wonderful shower head that after all the hustle and bustle from New York they can relax and fell rested for the next adventurous days in New York.
